story.title: Black Friday Scramble
story.storyDescription: Rachel: This is it! Only one more minute till they open!!!

author.bio: Author of THE TALE OF MU, a fantasy novel.

messages.text: This is it! Only one more minute till they open!!!
Why do we have to split up again?
So I can get a cart while you get a microwave
I’m sick of warming things up in the oven
Finally. We’ve only been waiting three hours
Don’t hurt anybody by accident when we get inside
Why? Cause I’m six foot five? ;)
If they’re smart they’d get outta my way
I can’t put my arms down
Hahaha!!!! I just saw some chick’s wig fly off
Can you see the home section?
I’m looking. What color? What color?
You sure you don’t want black??
They might have a cheap tablet
I could use it for the garage
Get back here!! Put the microwave in the cart
I left it on the floor of aisle six for you :)
Gonna see if I can snag a laptop
I’m not having sex with you till NEXT YEAR if you don’t come back now!!
Come here and help me put this in the cart
Some old lady just ran over my foot!!!
K. I’ll meet you in toys after I check if they have anymore silver ones?
But I’m sure the one we got’s gonna be fine
Maybe after we pay for it we can exchange it???
No, I see you poking around ELECTRONICS again!!
SOME WOMAN JUST SNATCHED THE MICROWAVE!!!!!!
Shouldn’t these kids be in school?
IDK, Charlie! I’ll be in toys, looking for whatever it’s called for your nephew
Is she wearing a white parka??
But yes. Yes!! She’s in a white parka
I just grabbed the second to last toy!!!
Have to hold it like a football
But I knocked her over by mistake
They have cameras!!! She could SUE!
She’s the one that stole it!
Meet me at the check stands
What about the skillet for my mom??
Look out for that kid on the ground!!
Did you drop the microwave AGAIN???!!
